'''Whitton Methodist Church'''  is a [[Methodist]] church on Percy Road, [[Whitton, London|Whitton]] in the [[London Borough of Richmond upon Thames]]. The church's minister is Rev. Claudia Lupi.<ref name="Circuit"/>

Services are held every Sunday at 10.30am, with [[Holy Communion]] once a month.<ref name="Circuit"/> '''Calvary Chapel Twickenham''' also uses the building for services.<ref name="Calvary">{{Cite web |url=http://www.calvarychapeltwickenham.com/meetings.asp |title=Weekly meetings |publisher=Calvary Chapel Twickenham}}</ref>

A hall at the church was badly damaged in a fire on 13 September 2015.<ref name="Fire">{{cite news | url=http://www.richmondandtwickenhamtimes.co.uk/news/13718363.Whitton_Methodist_Church_hall_engulfed_by_flames_in_Sunday_morning_fire/ | title=Whitton Methodist Church hall engulfed by flames in Sunday morning fire | work=[[Richmond and Twickenham Times]] | date=14 September 2015 | accessdate=14 September 2015 | author=Ambrose, Tom}}</ref>

